sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Player
    participant Game as Game Server
    participant LB as Leaderboard Service
    participant ZSET as Sorted Set Shard
    participant Log as Append-only Log
    participant Cache as Friends Cache

    Note over P,Cache: WRITE PATH (score event)
    P->>Game: report event (kills, lap time)
    Game->>Game: compute + sign score
    Game->>LB: POST /score {user, score, lb_id}
    LB->>Log: append write event
    Log-->>LB: ack durable
    LB->>ZSET: ZADD lb:daily:{date} score user
    ZSET-->>LB: ok
    LB-->>Game: 200

    Note over P,Cache: READ PATH (top-N)
    P->>LB: GET /top/{lb_id}?n=100
    LB->>ZSET: ZREVRANGE 0 99 WITHSCORES
    ZSET-->>LB: top 100 entries
    LB-->>P: ranked list

    Note over P,Cache: READ PATH (my rank + neighbors)
    P->>LB: GET /rank/{lb_id}/{user_id}
    alt single shard
        LB->>ZSET: ZREVRANK user
        ZSET-->>LB: rank, score
        LB->>ZSET: ZRANGEBYSCORE neighbors
        ZSET-->>LB: neighbor entries
    else score-range sharded (>10M users)
        LB->>ZSET: count higher shards + local rank
        ZSET-->>LB: aggregated rank
    end
    LB-->>P: {rank, score, neighbors}

    Note over P,Cache: FRIENDS LEADERBOARD (cached)
    P->>LB: GET /friends/{user_id}
    LB->>Cache: lookup cached ranking
    alt cache hit
        Cache-->>LB: sorted friends
    else cache miss
        LB->>ZSET: ZSCORE per friend (~200)
        ZSET-->>LB: scores
        LB->>LB: sort in memory
        LB->>Cache: store (TTL 5min)
    end
    LB-->>P: friends ranked
